    {"type":"text","id":"inj_1_t","x":1555,"y":1128,"width":690,"height":74,"text":"Assignment editor    /courses/:id/assignments/:aid/edit\n   →  inject  ✨ AI draft  button next to Save\n   →  opens BubbleTree panel  (unit · type · level · length)\n   target:  div#edit_assignment_form  →  mount above submit bar","originalText":"Assignment editor    /courses/:id/assignments/:aid/edit\n   →  inject  ✨ AI draft  button next to Save\n   →  opens BubbleTree panel  (unit · type · level · length)\n   target:  div#edit_assignment_form  →  mount above submit bar","fontSize":12,"fontFamily":3,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","strokeColor":"#1e40af","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"seed":681003,"version":1,"versionNonce":681004,"isDeleted":false,"groupIds":[],"boundElements":null,"link":null,"locked":false,"containerId":null,"lineHeight":1.45},

