    {"type":"text","id":"perm_h","x":120,"y":1715,"width":680,"height":24,"text":"manifest.json  —  permissions (minimal)","originalText":"manifest.json  —  permissions (minimal)","fontSize":16,"fontFamily":3,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","strokeColor":"#fbbf24","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"seed":690003,"version":1,"versionNonce":690004,"isDeleted":false,"groupIds":[],"boundElements":null,"link":null,"locked":false,"containerId":null,"lineHeight":1.25},
    {"type":"text","id":"perm_b","x":120,"y":1750,"width":680,"height":200,"text":"\"manifest_version\": 3,\n\"permissions\":         [ \"storage\", \"activeTab\" ],\n\"host_permissions\":    [ \"https://*.instructure.com/*\",\n                        \"https://api.canvasai.app/*\" ],\n\"externally_connectable\": { \"matches\": [ \"https://*.canvasai.app/*\" ] },\n\"content_scripts\":     [{ matches: [ \"https://*.instructure.com/*\" ],\n                        js: [ \"content/mount.ts\" ], run_at: \"document_idle\" }],\n\"background\":          { \"service_worker\": \"background/service_worker.ts\",\n                        \"type\": \"module\" },\n\"content_security_policy\": { \"extension_pages\": \"script-src 'self'; object-src 'self'\" }","originalText":"\"manifest_version\": 3,\n\"permissions\":         [ \"storage\", \"activeTab\" ],\n\"host_permissions\":    [ \"https://*.instructure.com/*\",\n                        \"https://api.canvasai.app/*\" ],\n\"externally_connectable\": { \"matches\": [ \"https://*.canvasai.app/*\" ] },\n\"content_scripts\":     [{ matches: [ \"https://*.instructure.com/*\" ],\n                        js: [ \"content/mount.ts\" ], run_at: \"document_idle\" }],\n\"background\":          { \"service_worker\": \"background/service_worker.ts\",\n                        \"type\": \"module\" },\n\"content_security_policy\": { \"extension_pages\": \"script-src 'self'; object-src 'self'\" }","fontSize":12,"fontFamily":3,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","strokeColor":"#22c55e","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"seed":690005,"version":1,"versionNonce":690006,"isDeleted":false,"groupIds":[],"boundElements":null,"link":null,"locked":false,"containerId":null,"lineHeight":1.55},

    {"type":"rectangle","id":"sec_ext","x":860,"y":1700,"width":720,"height":260,"strokeColor":"#334155","backgroundColor":"#1e293b","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"seed":691001,"version":1,"versionNonce":691002,"isDeleted":false,"groupIds":[],"boundElements":null,"link":null,"locked":false,"roundness":{"type":3}},
    {"type":"text","id":"sec_ext_h","x":880,"y":1715,"width":680,"height":24,"text":"Extension security posture","originalText":"Extension security posture","fontSize":16,"fontFamily":3,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","strokeColor":"#fbbf24","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"seed":691003,"version":1,"versionNonce":691004,"isDeleted":false,"groupIds":[],"boundElements":null,"link":null,"locked":false,"containerId":null,"lineHeight":1.25},
    {"type":"text","id":"sec_ext_b","x":880,"y":1750,"width":680,"height":200,"text":"•  Manifest V3: no remote code, no eval, no inline scripts. CSP enforced.\n•  PAT is NEVER stored in the extension — exchanged once at onboarding\n    for a short-lived JWT (15-min) + refresh token, both in chrome.storage.local.\n•  Canvas API calls on instructure.com use credentials:'include' (session cookie).\n    No token handoff from page context. Backend calls use the JWT.\n•  Content script and background share typed chrome.runtime.sendMessage;\n    every message is schema-validated (Zod) before dispatch.\n•  IndexedDB cache clears on sign-out, 7-day idle TTL, or on permissions revoke.\n•  externally_connectable restricts who can message us — only our web origin.\n•  Telemetry: no student content, only event_type + action_kind + duration.","originalText":"•  Manifest V3: no remote code, no eval, no inline scripts. CSP enforced.\n•  PAT is NEVER stored in the extension — exchanged once at onboarding\n    for a short-lived JWT (15-min) + refresh token, both in chrome.storage.local.\n•  Canvas API calls on instructure.com use credentials:'include' (session cookie).\n    No token handoff from page context. Backend calls use the JWT.\n•  Content script and background share typed chrome.runtime.sendMessage;\n    every message is schema-validated (Zod) before dispatch.\n•  IndexedDB cache clears on sign-out, 7-day idle TTL, or on permissions revoke.\n•  externally_connectable restricts who can message us — only our web origin.\n•  Telemetry: no student content, only event_type + action_kind + duration.","fontSize":12,"fontFamily":3,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","strokeColor":"#ffffff","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"seed":691005,"version":1,"versionNonce":691006,"isDeleted":false,"groupIds":[],"boundElements":null,"link":null,"locked":false,"containerId":null,"lineHeight":1.5},

    {"type":"rectangle","id":"tools","x":1620,"y":1700,"width":720,"height":260,"strokeColor":"#334155","backgroundColor":"#1e293b","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"seed":692001,"version":1,"versionNonce":692002,"isDeleted":false,"groupIds":[],"boundElements":null,"link":null,"locked":false,"roundness":{"type":3}},
    {"type":"text","id":"tools_h","x":1640,"y":1715,"width":680,"height":24,"text":"Stack  &  hackathon build plan","originalText":"Stack  &  hackathon build plan","fontSize":16,"fontFamily":3,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","strokeColor":"#fbbf24","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"seed":692003,"version":1,"versionNonce":692004,"isDeleted":false,"groupIds":[],"boundElements":null,"link":null,"locked":false,"containerId":null,"lineHeight":1.25},
    {"type":"text","id":"tools_b","x":1640,"y":1750,"width":680,"height":200,"text":"Extension   Vite  +  CRXJS  ·  React 18  ·  TypeScript strict  ·  Zod\nSite        Next.js 15 app-router  ·  shadcn/ui  ·  Tailwind  ·  React Query\nBackend     FastAPI  OR  Hono on Bun  ·  Anthropic SDK  ·  pdfplumber\nDB          Supabase  (Postgres 16 + pgvector)  ·  Drizzle ORM  ·  RLS on\nAuth        Supabase Auth  +  extension JWT  +  Canvas PAT vault\nLLM         Claude Opus 4.7 (authoring)  ·  Haiku 4.5 (scale/feedback)\nPayments    Stripe Billing  (Pro tier)  ·  manual PO on district\nHosting     Vercel (site)  ·  Fly.io or Cloudflare (backend)  ·  Supabase (db)\nTesting     Playwright against Free-for-Teachers sandbox","originalText":"Extension   Vite  +  CRXJS  ·  React 18  ·  TypeScript strict  ·  Zod\nSite        Next.js 15 app-router  ·  shadcn/ui  ·  Tailwind  ·  React Query\nBackend     FastAPI  OR  Hono on Bun  ·  Anthropic SDK  ·  pdfplumber\nDB          Supabase  (Postgres 16 + pgvector)  ·  Drizzle ORM  ·  RLS on\nAuth        Supabase Auth  +  extension JWT  +  Canvas PAT vault\nLLM         Claude Opus 4.7 (authoring)  ·  Haiku 4.5 (scale/feedback)\nPayments    Stripe Billing  (Pro tier)  ·  manual PO on district\nHosting     Vercel (site)  ·  Fly.io or Cloudflare (backend)  ·  Supabase (db)\nTesting     Playwright against Free-for-Teachers sandbox","fontSize":12,"fontFamily":3,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","strokeColor":"#22c55e","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"seed":692005,"version":1,"versionNonce":692006,"isDeleted":false,"groupIds":[],"boundElements":null,"link":null,"locked":false,"containerId":null,"lineHeight":1.55},

    {"type":"text","id":"footer2","x":80,"y":1990,"width":2240,"height":40,"text":"Sibling diagram to  canvas-ai-for-teachers.excalidraw  (product + business model). This file is strictly technical: database, extension framework, security, tooling.","originalText":"Sibling diagram to  canvas-ai-for-teachers.excalidraw  (product + business model). This file is strictly technical: database, extension framework, security, tooling.","fontSize":13,"fontFamily":3,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","strokeColor":"#64748b","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"seed":693001,"version":1,"versionNonce":693002,"isDeleted":false,"groupIds":[],"boundElements":null,"link":null,"locked":false,"containerId":null,"lineHeight":1.45}
